ing to go."],[1092,1209,"We're going to fuck this guy up."],[1234,1309,"Do you understand?"],[2306,2389,"Ok, ground crew."],[2431,2477,"Guess we're going to"],[2477,2556,"do this the hard way."],[2590,2794,"Break this motherfucker's legs."],[2844,3007,"And if anyone says anything about it,"],[3007,3128,"I'll pay the right people off."],[3161,3253,"Matter of fact,"],[3278,3390,"don't break this fucker's legs."],[3449,3678,"Kill this motherfucker now!"],[4049,4133,"Oh!"],[4971,5042,"What the hell do you"],[5042,5125,"think you're doing?"],[5134,5234,"Uncle Kane!"]],"30":[[0,120,"Oh, what the fuck?"],[120,400,"You don't get to call me uncle ever again."],[429,496,"What?"],[496,717,"And you just pissed off my boss."],[925,1242,"Mr. Hawkings, I am truly sorry"],[1242,1426,"for everything that transpired here today."],[1426,1534,"Uncle, what the hell?"],[1547,1810,"Are you telling me that this old fucking"],[1810,1968,"man is the owner of"],[1968,2085,"Maple fucking Airlines?"],[2085,2135,"There's no-"],[2193,2273,"Fuck me!"],[2289,2398,"Did you just call our boss"],[2398,2556,"a washed up old man?"],[2598,2723,"But, your boss?"],[2831,3036,"Your boss is a fucking baggage boy!"],[3036,3203,"He's a fucking nobody!"],[3236,3324,"Oh, fuck!"],[3349,3532,"Oh, fuck me!"],[3545,3691,"You are a goddamn fool!"],[3720,4024,"Your insane behavior towards Mr. Hawkings"],[4024,4275,"on his plane could have cost me my job."],[4337,4429,"I'm sorry, I'm sorry!"],[4446,4608,"I didn't know it was him, I swear!"],[4621,4713,"Can't let them fire you"],[4713,4779,"Enough!"]],"31":[[383,633,"Kane, Mr. Hawkings doesn't have time to"],[633,800,"watch you and your dipshit nephew"],[800,963,"bicker like boys on a playground."],[1009,1192,"So I suggest you drag him away from here"],[1192,1301,"before I have these guards"],[1301,1447,"beat you both to a pulp."],[1488,1639,"I'm sorry, I will escort him"],[1639,1768,"out of here immediately."],[1851,1956,"Let's go. - No, no, fuck!"],[1956,2135,"Fuck, okay! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!"],[2414,2577,"Are you alright, Mr. Hawkings?"],[2598,2765,"You're not hurt, are you?"],[2786,2865,"No, I'm fine."],[2936,3065,"Just an eventful evening."],[3119,3265,"Now, stop worrying about me."],[3365,3528,"And, uh, do me a favor."],[3561,3636,"Have a shuttle for"],[3636,3732,"the passengers on board."],[3799,3983,"I'm sure they are so exhausted after all"],[3983,4095,"they've been through."],[4129,4233,"Yes, sir."]],"32":[[450,621,"Thank you so much again for today."],[621,754,"If it wasn't for you, I-"],[834,1000,"I don't know what would have happened."],[1230,1317,"Glad I could help."],[1397,1685,"Actually, I wanted to ask you"],[1685,1835,"about something else."],[1960,2010,"What is it?"],[2114,2243,"Could you pretend to be"],[2243,2356,"my boyfriend tomorrow?"],[2456,2711,"Pretend to be, uh... your boyfriend."],[2994,3119,"You don't think I'm too old for you?"],[3169,3261,"I'm sure you've heard"],[3261,3440,"of the Grant family."],[3574,3737,"Well, I'm their sole heiress,"],[3737,3883,"and that's why my dad is"],[3883,4054,"pressuring me to marry."],[4104,4446,"But, I don't want to get married."],[4479,4708,"Hence the looking for a fake boyfriend."],[4721,4900,"I never would have guessed you were"],[4900,5105,"the Grant family heiress."]],"33":[[29,187,"The Grant family heiress."],[221,379,"It's a household name in New York."],[433,483,"Yeah."],[667,842,"Well, my dad told me that"],[846,992,"if I didn't bring a man home"],[996,1096,"within three years,"],[1096,1201,"he'd find me a groom."],[1288,1418,"And that was three years ago."],[1509,1622,"But none of the fake"],[1622,1768,"boyfriends I found are any good."],[1818,2001,"Every time they find out who my dad is,"],[2001,2173,"they freak and back out."],[2398,2506,"But you..."],[2669,2777,"you're different."],[3103,3224,"I don't think you would let"],[3224,3378,"a little storm unnerve you."],[3482,3528,"Little?"],[3645,3724,"Or big."],[3895,3999,"I think you're the only man"],[3999,4145,"who could win over my father."],[4291,4396,"I've never had an offer"],[4396,4504,"like this before."],[4704,4800,"I'll do it."],[5034,5138,"Really?"]],"34":[[12,108,"Really?"],[241,358,"Great."],[613,713,"There's just"],[784,909,"one more thing."],[1005,1117,"If you're going to pretend"],[1117,1263,"to be my boyfriend,"],[1263,1422,"you're going to have to act..."],[1547,1630,"rich."],[1864,1993,"Well,"],[1993,2293,"I am rich, so it should be easy."],[2344,2540,"Yes. Yes."],[2540,2790,"That's the exact vibe I'm going for."],[3028,3178,"I think there's still a bit of room"],[3178,3328,"for improvement, though."],[3541,3678,"Okay, how about this?"],[3691,3845,"Could you dress like,"],[3970,4116,"like you make nine figures?"],[4337,4416,"Nine figures?"],[4416,4633,"Yeah. Yeah. Like..."],[4733,5034,"Like your net worth is 300 million."],[5217,5330,"300 million?"],[5330,5430,"Yeah. Yeah."],[5430,5634,"Yeah, that's all I'm asking for."],[5634,5714,"Okay."],[5784,5947,"I'll see you here tomorrow"],[5968,6118,"at 2 PM, okay?"],[6210,6314,"Don't be late."],[6556,6669,"Thank you."],[7023,7136,"300 million."],[7194,7332,"I make that much in a day."],[7645,7803,"How am I supposed to downgrade?"]],"35":[[304,550,"Evelyn, I don't understand why you insist"],[558,658,"on being a flight attendant"],[658,742,"when you could be living"],[742,850,"your best life"],[850,921,"as the Grant"],[921,1009,"Family heiress."],[1009,1163,"I know, I mean, what do"],[1163,1313,"flight attendants make anyways?"],[1313,1434,"$50,000 a year?"],[1459,1618,"My husband gives me more"],[1618,1826,"in spending money each week."],[1872,1964,"See this bag?"],[1993,2227,"It's Chanel, limited edition."],[2248,2406,"My husband bought it for me,"],[2406,2565,"and there are only three of these"],[2565,2748,"on the entire planet Earth."],[2769,2927,"When you inherit your father's money,"],[2927,2994,"you're gonna be able"],[2994,3094,"to buy all three of those,"],[3094,3194,"and then some."],[3207,3424,"Wait, who said I'm going to"],[3424,3586,"inherit my father's fortune?"],[3666,3824,"I don't need my family's money."],[3887,4066,"Fine, but if you're not"],[4066,4183,"gonna take the inheritance"],[4183,4379,"for yourself, then at least find a"],[4379,4529,"handsome man to marry,"],[4533,4696,"pump out a few beautiful babies,"],[4704,4854,"And leave the money for them."],[4884,5042,"Slay! Yes, If you're trying"],[5042,5176,"to get away from your father,"],[5176,5267,"you might as well just"],[5267,5376,"have a family of your own."],[5413,5509,"What do I look like to you?"],[5509,5634,"A baby making machine?"],[5718,5910,"If my dad really wants an heir,"],[5910,6089,"then he can have a kid himself."],[6114,6302,"Ev, stop being so stubborn."],[6335,6464,"Okay, trust me,"],[6464,6569,"you're gonna like this next guy"],[6569,6660,"I'm setting you up with."],[6698,6794,"Girl, he's in finance,"],[6794,6923,"he's six-five, blue eyes,"],[6927,7107,"the works, if I didn't have a boyfriend,"],[7107,7240,"I would be all on that."],[7340,7490,"Well, ladies, actually,"],[7490,7607,"I already have a boyfriend."],[7657,7745,"What? - What?"],[7857,7916,"You have a - You have a"],[7916,8041,"boyfriend? - boyfriend?"],[8312,8671,"Ev, oh my God, okay, I love this for you."],[8671,8775,"You have to tell us"],[8775,8900,"which one of these elite families"],[8900,9021,"is he from, I mean,"],[9038,9142,"you have to introduce us!"],[9167,9501,"Yeah, well, he's a little older."]],"36":[[45,225,"But I'm already in love with him."],[367,658,"Okay, you'll like him. Let's go meet him."],[1222,1401,"Mr. Hawkings?"],[2102,2235,"Yeah, where is he?"],[2252,2494,"Making three absolute hotties like us"],[2494,2648,"wait around in a garage?"],[2669,2852,"Oh, some gentleman he is."],[3661,3891,"Uh, why is that phone ringing?"],[4045,4241,"Hello? Oh! Oh, jeez!"],[4241,4446,"This mechanic is a fucking creep!"],[4496,4621,"You disgusting pervert!"],[4679,4850,"I'm sorry, I did not mean to."],[4900,5005,"Yeah, right, we all saw you"],[5005,5142,"you greasy old fuck."],[5213,5434,"I'm gonna gouge your goddamn eyes out."],[5547,5726,"Miss, I promise I wasn't trying"],[5726,5868,"to do anything."],[5968,6101,"Tell that to the cops."],[6177,6293,"Mr. Hawkings."],[6318,6506,"Wait, you know him?"]],"37":[[112,287,"Mr. Hawkings,"],[325,533,"what were you doing under the car?"],[663,880,"Well, I got here early and thought"],[880,1030,"I'd take the car for a quick spin."],[1076,1192,"When I got back, you weren't here,"],[1192,1317,"so I though I'd check the engine."],[1343,1664,"But, Mr. Hawkings, I thought I told you"],[1664,1860,"to dress like a rich man,"],[1910,2014,"and not somebody who"],[2014,2152,"fixes cars for a living."],[2198,2339,"Yeah, you told me my net worth was"],[2339,2435,"supposed to be $300 million?"],[2506,2619,"Yes, yes."],[2698,2915,"So, what on earth made you think that"],[2915,3082,"scruffy mechanic was the right look?"],[3224,3424,"$300 million is what I pay my engineer."],[3457,3695,"This fits exactly what you asked for."],[3766,3828,"Right."],[3870,4295,"Um, I was just really counting on you."],[4333,4521,"If you pay your engineer so much money,"],[4521,4683,"wouldn't he have nicer clothes?"],[4717,4888,"Evelyn, this is his jumpsuit."],[4917,5017,"I stopped by his place"],[5017,5117,"to pick it up on the way here."],[5176,5288,"I thought this is what you wanted."],[5438,5730,"Ev, you aren't actually telling us"],[5730,5976,"that you know this dirt broke mechanic."],[6260,6527,"Well, I don't just know him."],[6702,6777,"He's my boyfriend."],[6819,6877,"What? -What?"]],"38":[[75,233,"So, that billionaire"],[233,392,"that you were telling me about?"],[408,508,"That man?"],[588,721,"It's him?"],[767,880,"The grease monkey?"],[1005,1263,"Well, guys, I know he's a little bit"],[1309,1443,"rough around the edges,"],[1443,1751,"but he's stacked like..."],[1751,1864,"Jeff Bezos."],[1868,2114,"This guy has that kind of money?"],[2210,2369,"I mean, is that so hard to believe?"],[2385,2606,"I'm a highly sought after engineer."],[2802,2965,"Yeah, freaking right."],[3002,3194,"I mean, all I see standing in front of me"],[3203,3370,"is an oily old repairman."],[3390,3499,"Screw this. This mechanic"],[3499,3778,"has to be some kind of Tinder Swindler."],[3778,3987,"I’ve got to expose him!"],[3987,4275,"Ev, you can't actually be serious"],[4275,4533,"that you know this dirt broke mechanic?"],[4629,4721,"Evelyn."],[4721,4817,"Come here, babe."],[4917,5238,"So, you're the Grant family heiress."],[5376,5543,"You have billions"],[5543,5693,"coming into your lap."],[5734,5843,"Potentially."],[5851,5985,"What are you doing"],[6022,6214,"with this grease monkey?"],[6272,6493,"I think we're a perfect match."],[6606,6927,"And I like him, and I want to be with him"],[6927,7119,"so there's that."],[7282,7369,"Okay."],[7390,7545,"Well, if you have so much"],[7545,7711,"fuck you money then,"],[7786,7932,"why didn't you bring any gifts"],[7932,8066,"for your girlfriend's cousins?"],[8087,8337,"Selena? That's a little rude."],[8383,8454,"No, no, she's right."],[8479,8566,"It would be impolite"],[8566,8729,"for me to show up empty-handed."],[8896,9084,"Of course I brought gifts for family."]],"39":[[108,246,"I wonder what that piece of shit"],[246,400,"swindler mechanic got us."],[2873,2973,"Sir."],[3073,3299,"Ladies, I present the newest"],[3299,3536,"limited edition Chanel handbags."],[3545,3636,"There are only three of these"],[3636,3762,"in the whole wide world."],[3945,4133,"Um, Crystal,"],[4250,4358,"why do these three bags"],[4358,4542,"look identical to yours?"],[4575,4929,"No. My husband bought me this bag."],[5042,5142,"I know."],[5376,5668,"You dirty, broke-ass grease monkey."]],"40":[[54,304,"First, you lie to Evelyn and say that"],[304,496,"you're rich just so she'll date you."],[496,638,"And now you show up here with these"],[638,809,"fake goods and shitty"],[809,988,"knockoff bags as gifts?"],[1059,1313,"These are real. My secretary personally"],[1313,1514,"delivered them to me just yesterday."],[1584,1743,"Did he just say he has"],[1743,1889,"a secretary, of all things?"],[1968,2173,"This dirty, low-down grease monkey"],[2173,2264,"would never have"],[2264,2452,"a secretary. That's crazy."],[2623,2777,"Trust me, I insist."],[3082,3253,"Evelyn, where the hell"],[3253,3382,"did you find this guy?"],[3453,3670,"I mean, it'd be one thing if he didn't"],[3670,3816,"provide us with gifts."],[3828,3912,"We could chalk it up to"],[3912,4037,"him being forgetful or poor."],[4104,4308,"But to show up here with these fake"],[4308,4496,"goods in order to try and trick us?"],[4525,4629,"That just proves"],[4629,4788,"he's trying to swindle your fortune."]],"41":[[0,154,"That just proves he's trying"],[154,342,"to swindle your fortune."],[371,475,"Listen, I am not"],[475,633,"trying to swindle anybody."],[704,913,"See, my secretary had these bags"],[942,1134,"delivered on a private jet straight from"],[1134,1238,"the Chanel headquarters"],[1238,1330,"in London."],[1372,1580,"But these are as real as it gets."],[1651,1864,"And what? My bag is fake then?"],[1910,2164,"Listen, dumbass. See this?"],[2164,2356,"My husband bought me this bag."],[2356,2510,"There are supposed to be only three of these"],[2510,2660,"on the entire planet Earth."],[2660,2907,"But here, in this garage there are four"],[2936,3282,"Witch means your bags, are knockoffs."],[3311,3503,"Ev, come on. It's clear that this man"],[3503,3632,"is playing you for a fool."],[3678,3766,"Alright."],[3858,4029,"You don't believe the bags are real?"],[4124,4275,"I'll confirm it."],[4871,5042,"Bonjour, Mr. Hawkings."],[5071,5134,"Lafayette,"],[5134,5267,"viens tout de suite"],[5267,5497,"et authentifiez ces sacs pour moi?"],[5768,6051,"Bah oui, sir, got it."],[6193,6293,"Forget it, creep. Just take"],[6293,6489,"your knockoff bags and get out."],[7336,7557,"It's raining money!"],[7574,7741,"How can a regular mechanic"],[7741,7874,"have so much money?"],[8020,8316,"Sir, why is there cash in that bag?"]],"42":[[12,383,"Sir, why is there cash in this bag?"],[429,604,"Well, I didn't think the simple handbag"],[604,709,"would be quite enough,"],[709,779,"and I didn't have"],[779,863,"enough time to prepare,"],[863,1184,"so I added a little extra on top of it."],[1263,1351,"But, sir."],[1393,1568,"This is, this is too much."],[1659,1826,"It's nothing, really."],[1889,2164,"Ok, this has to be fake, too."],[2189,2314,"All right, I've had enough"],[2314,2410,"with this man."],[2423,2544,"First, your background's fake."],[2544,2648,"Your job's fake."],[2665,2873,"I bet you your hair's not even real."],[2898,2986,"Selena!"],[3002,3061,"Huh."],[3098,3224,"At least his hair's real."],[3274,3453,"As real as the money on the floor."],[3478,3586,"Yeah, back to that."],[3591,3712,"You keep tricking us."],[3737,3912,"Ev, this guy is no good."],[3937,4012,"Ditch him."],[4129,4371,"I promise, everything is real."],[4371,4508,"Just look closely."],[4546,4783,"I, I think this is real."],[4884,4979,"Well, if it is real,"],[4979,5117,"he probably robbed someone."],[5463,5697,"Well, I'm still calling the cops."],[6160,6335,"Bonjour, Mr. Hawkings."],[6685,6844,"Ah, what the fuck?"],[6865,6981,"That's Lafayette Price."],[7011,7157,"That's Chanel's lead designer."]],"43":[[396,563,"Mr. Hawkings, you called"],[563,684,"and I'm right here."],[738,863,"Lafayette, quick question."],[863,925,"Mm-hmm?"],[925,1084,"Those bags you gave me yesterday,"],[1109,1209,"you said there was only"],[1209,1347,"three in the whole world."],[1368,1438,"That's right, sir."],[1455,1618,"We've only made three of these bags"],[1634,1739,"and we gave them all to you."],[1843,1997,"Well then, why is there"],[1997,2248,"a fourth right there?"],[2519,2648,"Pardon, madame, but would you mind"],[2648,2794,"if I took a look at your bag?"],[2952,3028,"Merci."],[3103,3390,"Ooh, la la, these counterfeits"],[3390,3549,"just keep getting worse and worse."],[3549,3645,"Unbelievable."],[3666,3853,"Mr. Hawkings, this is truly"],[3853,4020,"an awful knockoff."],[4037,4250,"The stitch work is amateur at best"],[4283,4517,"and they did not even get the logo right."],[4600,4788,"But my husband bought me that bag."],[4788,4946,"He would never get me a fake bag!"],[4967,5121,"Madame, a man who buys you"],[5121,5288,"cheap trash like this"],[5288,5434,"isn't worth your time."],[5480,5684,"If I were you, I'd get"],[5684,5935,"those divorce papers ready."],[5985,6056,"Okay."],[6135,6218,"Lafayette,"],[6268,6381,"merci pour donnée."],[6452,6539,"À bientôt."],[6569,6685,"Au revoir."],[7178,7248,"Do you believe me now?"],[7682,7824,"Whoa, whoa, whoa."],[7824,8062,"Who started the party without me?"]],"44":[[291,467,"Evelyn, this is Xavier."],[500,604,"He's the hotshot race car driver"],[604,717,"I was telling you about."],[779,942,"So, you're Evelyn."],[1076,1247,"And you must be her father."],[1484,1789,"Xavier, no, this is not Evelyn's father."],[1910,1993,"He's not?"],[2047,2306,"Then why do they look so... close?"],[2602,2719,"Because he's my boyfriend."],[2723,2840,"Boyfriend?"],[2840,3086,"Evelyn, what the fuck is going on here?"],[3090,3269,"Uh, what, do I need"],[3269,3436,"your permission to date someone?"],[3461,3745,"Evelyn, I come here today to see you,"],[3762,3937,"and you bring this wrinkly old boomer"],[3937,4120,"who you claim is your boyfriend?"],[4162,4383,"Are you trying to embarrass me?"]],"45":[[29,246,"Are you trying to embarrass me?"],[262,387,"What does me being her boyfriend"],[387,504,"have to do with you?"],[525,621,"Shut it, old fart."],[704,850,"I don't waste my breath"],[850,1063,"answering no-name mechanics."],[1413,1597,"Listen, old man,"],[1597,1780,"either you break it off with Evelyn,"],[1818,2097,"or I make you disappear overnight."],[2110,2198,"What's it gonna be?"],[2206,2314,"Ha ha ha!"],[2352,2544,"Xavier's from one of the top families"],[2544,2648,"in New York City."],[2686,2836,"If you don't do what he says,"],[2836,2977,"he'll fucking finish you."],[2977,3107,"Evelyn, are you for real?"],[3169,3282,"Xavier's got it all."],[3290,3420,"He's young, he's handsome,"],[3420,3570,"he's got a lot going for him."],[3636,3903,"What does Josh, John..."],[3958,4029,"Jett."],[4054,4229,"Whatever, have that he doesn't?"],[4258,4437,"He's got.. all together?"],[4437,4637,"All I see is a pathetic jerk"],[4637,4788,"who's running around"],[4788,4929,"spending his daddy's money"],[4929,5130,"on gambling, hookers and drugs."],[5155,5326,"Oh, so what's a little fun?"],[5347,5497,"You know, work hard, play hard."],[5547,5805,"Besides, check this out."],[5868,6126,"Xavier finished a lap in 38 seconds."],[6202,6343,"That's one of the top 10"],[6343,6560,"lap times of the racetrack."],[6731,6915,"Wow, 38 seconds?"],[6973,7082,"Xavier, you're gonna be"],[7082,7286,"a NASCAR star in no time."],[7386,7515,"38 second lap time"],[7515,7741,"is... not bad on this track."],[7828,7924,"See, when I was younger,"],[7924,8078,"I was doing laps faster than that"],[8078,8224,"without breaking a sweat."],[8258,8429,"But you know, I guess there's"],[8429,8554,"always improvement for..."],[8662,8758,"a novice like you."]],"46":[[33,91,"I guess there's"],[91,225,"always improvement for..."],[271,367,"a novice like you."],[437,688,"Faster than 38 seconds?"],[704,880,"Give me a break, old man."],[955,1209,"That screen shows the top times"],[1209,1380,"ever recorded at this racetrack."],[1484,1685,"If you were really faster, your name"],[1685,1847,"would be above mine."],[1914,2031,"Stop being mean to him."],[2081,2177,"He, he saved me."],[2227,2344,"Many times!"],[2344,2435,"Saved you?"],[2469,2681,"So, old man,"],[2756,3007,"you really think you're a speed star?"],[3199,3269,"Do a lap."],[3365,3424,"Prove it."],[3520,3666,"I don't need to prove anything."],[3766,3883,"See that screen?"],[3949,4133,"The time at the top of the list is mine."],[4562,4717,"The top of the list?"],[4725,4888,"29 seconds?"],[4904,5096,"So you're saying that you got the top"],[5096,5238,"recorded speed in history"],[5246,5451,"here at Godspeed Racetrack?"]],"47":[[0,191,"The top recorded speed in history"],[191,404,"here at Godspeed Racetrack?"],[500,625,"Well, that's not all."],[754,980,"Back in the day, my name used to fill"],[980,1151,"every spot on that leaderboard."],[1167,1288,"But as I got older,"],[1288,1472,"I started taking my foot off the gas."],[1480,1659,"I wanted to give young hotshots"],[1659,1810,"like you a chance to shine."],[1960,2077,"That's hilarious."],[2110,2381,"So you're saying you used to be a racer?"],[2544,2752,"Come on, you're just a filthy repairman."],[2752,2927,"When could you even afford your own car?"],[2932,3123,"A car? This old man"],[3123,3303,"can't even afford a used bike."],[3470,3703,"Ev, your senior citizen boyfriend"],[3703,3862,"is a pathological liar."],[3908,4041,"Can't trust a thing he says."],[4241,4371,"Mr. Hawkings,"],[4416,4554,"you don't have to put up an act."],[4592,4713,"You can just be yourself."],[4859,4979,"I am being myself."],[5013,5159,"Congratulations to Xavier Gordon"],[5159,5301,"on recording a top 10 lap time"],[5301,5476,"in the history of Godspeed Racetrack!"],[5476,5609,"As a reward, he will receive"],[5609,5714,"a generous cash prize"],[5714,5889,"of $10 million."]],"48":[[41,321,"Oh my God, congrats, Xavier!"],[367,487,"There hasn't been a name"],[492,667,"on the top ten list in over a decade."],[809,1046,"Trust me, I'm just getting started."],[1893,2118,"Jeez, a 38 second lap time is only good"],[2118,2243,"for tenth of all time?"],[2293,2464,"Whoever has the times before must be"],[2464,2577,"a generational talent."],[2631,2794,"Those are the guys from yesterday,"],[2794,2915,"but I'm up now."],[2973,3082,"And you better believe,"],[3115,3265,"I'm coming for their heads."],[3415,3578,"Yeah, see that old man?"],[3578,3661,"Is Xavier's name"],[3661,3824,"going down in history."],[3824,3928,"Who the fuck are you"],[3928,4054,"to compare yourself to him?"],[4108,4416,"Mr. Hawkings, I was trying to tell you,"],[4416,4642,"you can't keep up this act forever."],[4863,4934,"Just look."],[5017,5230,"What a joke! This old man"],[5230,5509,"fixes cars. I race them."],[5572,5680,"Just look."]],"49":[[166,241,"What?"],[287,521,"Why do they all say Jett?"],[633,892,"What did you do, you old schmuck?"],[946,1134,"You probably paid someone"],[1134,1305,"to fix the rankings, didn't you?"],[1326,1559,"Has it not occurred to you that maybe"],[1601,1730,"those lap times are really mine?"],[1739,1830,"Honestly, it's impressive"],[1830,1901,"you were even able"],[1901,2043,"to make a top ten time"],[2043,2285,"with an... entry level race car."],[2302,2494,"Entry level racecar?"],[2565,2786,"If you are going to claim to be a racer,"],[2786,2894,"you better know the first thing"],[2894,2977,"about cars."],[2990,3249,"This is a Jaguar i7."],[3274,3411,"Custom."],[3420,3687,"I dropped five million bucks on it."],[3695,3866,"This old geezer who fixes cars"],[3866,4033,"can't tell a gem when he sees one."],[4058,4200,"The only thing he should be repairing"],[4200,4337,"is his own brain."],[4654,4821,"I've driven this Jaguar before."],[4821,4888,"The handling on it"],[4888,5034,"is some of the worst I've ever seen."],[5084,5230,"I'm actually surprised a beginner like you"],[5230,5355,"didn't crash it."],[5355,5651,"Did I just hear a greasy old repairman"],[5651,6031,"refer to me, a prize winning racer,"],[6031,6189,"as a beginner?"],[6202,6460,"Just you wait, buddy. I'm going to buy"],[6460,6585,"a new car and when I do,"],[6585,6752,"my name is going to shoot"],[6752,6877,"to the top of the chart."],[6981,7082,"New car, huh?"],[7207,7315,"Let me know if you need any help."],[7315,7444,"I'd be more than happy"],[7444,7603,"to contact a dealership for you."],[7632,8037,"That's hilarious. I'm friends with Ivan,"],[8049,8454,"the top racecar dealership in Vegas."],[8529,8754,"The last thing I need is your help."]],"50":[[25,229,"The last thing I need is your help."],[296,437,"You're friends with Ivan?"],[483,717,"The billionaire who gets exclusive sales"],[717,917,"to the newest top tier race cars?"],[1026,1080,"Wow."],[1117,1284,"I didn't know you knew Ivan."],[1343,1493,"Yeah, go ahead, give him a call."],[1526,1630,"I'm looking to buy a"],[1630,1735,"new car from him too."],[1735,1856,"Fuck. I shouldn't have"],[1910,2122,"talked such a big game."],[2122,2218,"I've only brushed shoulders"],[2218,2352,"with Ivan once,"],[2352,2556,"and we didn't even speak."],[2556,2656,"If I call this guy,"],[2715,2819,"he'll expose me."],[2840,2927,"Or..."],[3011,3128,"do you not have his number?"],[3174,3261,"What?"],[3319,3582,"Ivan and I are day ones."],[3799,3983,"And you say you want to buy a new car?"],[3983,4108,"Can you even afford one"],[4108,4316,"with your meager mechanic salary?"],[4362,4596,"Weird. Went straight to voicemail."],[4675,4838,"Probably has his phone off."],[4838,5000,"I'll talk to him next time."],[5000,5142,"I wanted to meet the legend."],[5251,5384,"I mean, meeting Ivan"],[5384,5643,"in real life would be so surreal."],[5689,5960,"But it's probably for the best that Ivan"],[5960,6143,"doesn't see this"],[6143,6327,"disgusting mechanic anyways."],[6385,6510,"He can't be associating and"],[6510,6777,"mingling with such a repairman."],[6877,7027,"Let's give Ivan a call,"],[7040,7353,"see if he agrees."]],"51":[[75,158,"Ivan."],[291,504,"Yeah, it's me. Listen,"],[550,750,"can you come by the racetrack?"],[750,867,"Yeah, I'm with a guy who"],[900,1046,"really wants to buy a car from you."],[1101,1280,"Yeah, and actually,"],[1305,1443,"I was thinking about buying a new car"],[1443,1584,"from you myself."],[1651,1751,"Yeah, the racetrack."],[1864,2077,"Great. I'll see you soon."],[2114,2239,"That..."],[2289,2594,"was an Oscar worthy performance."],[2744,2969,"Thank you. Oscar worthy."],[2969,3199,"Oh, please. If Ivan didn't answer"],[3199,3390,"the phone for Xavier, why would he"],[3390,3520,"answer the phone for you?"],[3549,3741,"Guys, this grease monkey is"],[3741,3899,"running us through a loop."],[3937,4108,"He probably wasn't even on the phone."],[4154,4391,"Just standing there talking to no one."],[4450,4625,"You think so?"],[4654,4888,"Well, when Ivan shows up"],[4888,5030,"in the next few minutes,"],[5100,5226,"let's just see if I was"],[5226,5326,"still talking to myself."],[5363,5513,"In the next few minutes?"],[5547,5697,"Who the hell are you"],[5697,5901,"to claim that you know Ivan?"]],"52":[[95,287,"Let's just wait and see."],[287,371,"I've had enough"],[371,575,"of your empty posturing, buddy."],[617,825,"That guy is my brother"],[825,984,"from another mother."],[984,1176,"So, I know him well enough"],[1176,1405,"than to ask him to carve out time"],[1405,1526,"in his busy schedule"],[1547,1676,"to come down here"],[1676,1851,"to this dusty garage."],[1881,2027,"If you think that he's going to drop"],[2027,2214,"everything to meet you,"],[2214,2398,"you're out of your goddamn mind."],[2615,2819,"He's right. Ivan's a multi-billionaire."],[2819,3032,"He's got places to go and people to see."],[3069,3282,"He can't just be seen mingling here with"],[3282,3474,"you, dirt old repairman."],[3541,3712,"Ivan always makes time for me."],[3737,3862,"I brought a lot of business to his"],[3862,4029,"dealership for the past few years."],[4041,4183,"It's the least he can do."],[4195,4521,"Like what? Asking for car parts?"],[4612,4954,"I mean, I must have bought like 25 cars"],[4954,5121,"or so within the last few years."],[5397,5613,"Okay, you've bought 25 cars from him?"],[5613,5689,"What do you mean?"],[5689,5797,"In, like, Hot Wheels?"],[5926,6051,"Evelyn, I'm getting tired"],[6051,6185,"of your boyfriend's shit."],[6206,6477,"Either he shuts his mouth or we leave."]],"53":[[246,371,"Ivan."],[458,554,"Nice to see you."],[571,713,"Hi, it's so nice to meet you."],[713,896,"Hi, it's nice to meet you."],[988,1176,"Mr. Hawkings, it's been a while."],[1188,1276,"Ivan."],[1317,1405,"I don't understand,"],[1405,1522,"why did he just go right"],[1522,1634,"past Xavier and go"],[1634,1764,"straight to this slime ball?"],[1780,1860,"Yeah, I thought you guys"],[1860,2001,"were supposed to be friends."],[2052,2118,"So..."],[2210,2306,"So did I."],[2339,2456,"Ivan, now..."],[2489,2590,"this guy behind you,"],[2590,2752,"he tried calling you,"],[2752,2886,"but it went straight to voicemail."],[2994,3111,"What was that about?"],[3169,3282,"Oh, that, yes."],[3332,3432,"I get a lot of calls"],[3432,3578,"from small time racers"],[3578,3670,"who are too broke"],[3670,3782,"to actually afford a car."],[3837,3941,"Eventually I got sick of it,"],[3941,4124,"so I stopped answering altogether."],[4254,4446,"But Ivan, I mean,"],[4446,4567,"you picked up right away when"],[4629,4733,"I called you."],[4733,4829,"Of course."],[4867,5013,"That's because you're you."],[5046,5184,"I have a separate phone"],[5184,5296,"and a separate phone number"],[5296,5401,"just for when you call."],[5463,5576,"No one else even has it."],[5772,5851,"Classic Ivan."],[5943,6031,"Well, you've always known"],[6031,6181,"how to treat your top clients."],[6214,6373,"That's what sets your business apart."],[6389,6506,"Absolutely, Mr. Hawkings."],[6556,6698,"So you said that you were"],[6698,6819,"in the market for a new car."],[6840,7044,"Did you have anything particular in mind?"],[7152,7315,"Yeah, well I like the look"],[7315,7440,"of the latest Lamborghini."],[7503,7561,"Didn't you just get"],[7561,7657,"the first one in stock?"],[7657,7720,"Why don't you have someone"],[7720,7799,"send it over?"],[7799,7907,"Absolutely, we'll take care"],[7907,7999,"of that right away."],[8062,8141,"Thank you, Ivan."],[8191,8341,"Oh, and Xavier here also"],[8341,8483,"wants to buy a car from you."],[8583,8671,"Xavier? Who's that?"],[8733,8913,"Ah, well, that guy."],[8967,9084,"Said you two were"],[9117,9267,"brothers from another mother?"],[9463,9559,"Who the hell is that?"]],"54":[[0,250,"I'm Xavier. Don't you remember me?"],[271,371,"Xavier..."],[417,604,"No. Anyway, you said you were"],[604,692,"looking for a car."],[692,842,"What kind of car would you like?"],[863,1005,"Yeah. Do you have any"],[1005,1163,"Porsche 718s in stock?"],[1188,1305,"No, we don't carry those."],[1372,1534,"Alright. Do you have"],[1534,1676,"the newest Gran Turismo?"],[1714,1960,"Yeah. That would also be a no."],[1968,2239,"Sir, forgive my bluntness, but you run"],[2239,2414,"the top dealership in the States."],[2414,2544,"Shouldn't you offer"],[2544,2694,"a wider selection?"],[2694,2765,"Listen."],[2806,3003,"Sean, Cody, Zach-"],[3003,3065,"Xavier."],[3082,3194,"Whatever your name is."],[3236,3390,"My dealership only sells"],[3424,3620,"uber-luxury supercars."],[3674,3803,"Just compare the cars"],[3803,3970,"that Mr. Hawkings buys"],[3970,4104,"to the ones that you're talking about,"],[4104,4233,"and I think you'll see the difference."],[4233,4320,"The bottom line is,"],[4325,4521,"if you only have one or two million"],[4521,4808,"dollars to spend, then perhaps you should"],[4808,4950,"take your business somewhere else."]],"55":[[112,291,"Mr. Hawkings, is he saying"],[291,479,"that a $2 million car"],[479,633,"is not a deal for his dealership?"],[713,896,"Yeah, pretty much all of"],[921,1167,"Ivan's cars run $10 million or more."],[1167,1263,"10 million?"],[1263,1413,"That's insane."],[1530,1664,"Well then, Ivan's dealership"],[1664,1768,"definitely doesn't have anything"],[1768,1872,"on Xavier's budget."],[1918,1993,"Fine."],[1993,2102,"I don't need your"],[2102,2214,"shitty dealership anyway."],[2218,2339,"I'll just go to another place"],[2339,2464,"with more variety."],[2494,2686,"If you had told me that you only had a"],[2686,2894,"$1 or $2 million budget,"],[2894,3003,"then I would have sent you"],[3003,3194,"to any old run of the mill"],[3194,3428,"auto dealer, instead of standing here,"],[3440,3737,"wasting my time."],[4012,4108,"Mr. Hawkings,"],[4108,4229,"we will have your Lamborghini"],[4229,4362,"delivered to you right away."],[4408,4546,"Ivan, it's always a pleasure."],[4546,4696,"Thank you, sir."],[5046,5176,"If you and Ivan are friends,"],[5176,5271,"why did he completely"],[5271,5367,"ignore you?"]],"56":[[0,108,"Uh, well..."],[216,471,"Guys? Isn't it obvious?"],[579,775,"Xavier and Ivan were never friends."],[775,938,"He didn't even know him."],[950,1101,"He was just lying to us."],[1138,1326,"Why would Xavier lie to us?"],[1326,1526,"You know what's more possible?"],[1564,1747,"is the person that was just here"],[1747,1864,"isn't even the real Ivan."],[1876,2035,"Yeah, that's exactly it."],[2052,2235,"That wasn't even the real Ivan."],[2256,2485,"Okay, um, yeah."],[2544,2631,"Who was he then?"],[2631,2773,"How should we know?"],[2786,2919,"You probably picked up"],[2927,3023,"a random impersonator"],[3023,3123,"off the street."],[3207,3449,"Wow, I mean, honestly, I am..."],[3486,3591,"I'm impressed."],[3591,3766,"I mean, the mental gymnastics"],[3766,4049,"on display here are truly remarkable."],[4066,4216,"Cut the bullshit!"],[4216,4337,"Here's the truth:"],[4337,4521,"you're a piss-poor auto mechanic"],[4521,4704,"who used his entire month's salary,"],[4704,4896,"hiring some guy of the street to come"],[4896,5050,"here and make you look cool."],[5075,5163,"So..."],[5230,5355,"stop acting big and copping"],[5355,5505,"that you got a Lamborghini"],[5505,5668,"when we know the truth that"],[5668,5876,"you're a fucking bike commuter!"],[6569,6752,"Mr. Hawkings, the car you requested"],[6752,6894,"has arrived at the track. Would you like"],[6894,7015,"to take it for a test drive?"],[7115,7315,"Absolutely. Bring it to the garage."],[7511,7937,"So, that was your new Lamborghini?"],[8049,8183,"Man, he's gonna look like an idiot"],[8183,8337,"when that never shows up."]],"57":[[446,583,"Oh my God!"],[604,738,"Okay, this can't be happening."],[759,859,"No fricking way."],[859,967,"This just dropped in the market"],[967,1134,"for like 30 million dollars."],[1159,1280,"I can't believe this"],[1280,1430,"mechanic had that kind of pull."],[1463,1618,"Mr. Hawkings, is this really"],[1618,1755,"the car you're buying?"],[1843,1910,"That's right."],[1997,2193,"But it costs $30 million."],[2252,2389,"How could you buy it"],[2389,2502,"without even batting an eye?"],[2585,2781,"That's a mid-range purchase for me."],[2827,2986,"I have plenty of cars in my collection."],[3036,3157,"No fucking way!"],[3178,3336,"I refuse to believe"],[3336,3574,"that this garage worker"],[3616,3782,"could afford this car."],[3816,3883,"Who's it for?"],[3937,4008,"You?"],[4008,4133,"The point is,"],[4133,4220,"this isn't yours."],[4279,4479,"Look at you in your greasy jumpsuit."],[4542,4667,"A guy like you would"],[4667,4829,"never get behind the wheel"],[4829,4959,"of a car like that."]],"58":[[37,271,"Xavier, Mr. Hawkings bought it from Ivan,"],[296,442,"right in front of your eyes."],[504,646,"How can you still not believe him?"],[704,846,"That wasn't the real Ivan."],[846,900,"I knew"],[917,992,"an auto mechanic"],[992,1055,"like you"],[1055,1113,"couldn't afford"],[1117,1288,"a $30 million race car like that."],[1326,1472,"This is just all part of your charade"],[1472,1618,"to show off your fuck you money."],[1701,1780,"Really?"],[1868,2147,"And to think I almost fell for your lies."],[2223,2444,"Mr. Hawkings already has proven himself."],[2502,2627,"If you don't believe him,"],[2627,2752,"then I don't know what to tell you."],[2794,2936,"He didn't prove fucking shit."],[2965,3144,"You know, I got an idea."],[3244,3553,"This car has the new AI hologram"],[3553,3682,"built into it, doesn't it?"],[3812,4066,"Well, if it's really your car,"],[4129,4341,"only you would be able to activate it."],[4366,4521,"Yes, I should."],[4662,4804,"Rise and shine, Lambo."],[5042,5130,"Hello!"],[5163,5305,"How may I help you?"]],"59":[[37,279,"Lambo, come here."],[709,767,"Oh my God."],[838,921,"That's the coolest"],[921,1071,"feature I've ever seen in a car."],[1159,1259,"It's the first Lamborghini"],[1259,1455,"with a speech recognition system."],[1651,1814,"So do you believe me now?"],[1856,1943,"Oh, come on."],[1943,2022,"Big deal."],[2035,2122,"All it proves is that"],[2122,2239,"the voice recognition works."],[2264,2394,"It just proves that"],[2394,2527,"it's working properly."],[2590,2711,"Xavier, really?"],[2727,2886,"It doesn't just recognize"],[2886,2973,"any voice."],[3007,3203,"It works for the owner, no one else."],[3249,3319,"Fine."],[3328,3503,"It is his car."],[3511,3636,"What kind of man would buy"],[3636,3762,"this Barbie Land bullshit?"],[3807,3928,"Who are you to judge"],[3928,4104,"what colors Mr. Hawkings likes?"],[4158,4241,"This is the one"],[4241,4416,"they had in stock, pink."],[4462,4537,"It's probably the first one"],[4537,4654,"that hit the market."],[4658,4746,"Or maybe he didn't have"],[4746,4900,"enough money to customize it."],[4934,5125,"Or more like"],[5125,5284,"he's renting the car."],[5367,5555,"Well, either way, you shouldn't doubt him"],[5563,5734,"based on something so trivial."],[5780,5960,"I don't give a fuck what you say."],[5985,6185,"This is a woman's car."],[6322,6477,"Finally you said something right."],[6502,6715,"This car is for a woman."]],"60":[[29,191,"Ha! He did admit it!"],[191,362,"See? This car isn't his!"],[412,604,"The old man finally ran out of tricks."],[638,750,"Took him long enough."],[763,942,"Evelyn, what do you think of this car?"],[1267,1397,"I love it."],[1488,1568,"It's yours."],[1710,1793,"Mine?"],[1810,2014,"Go ahead and talk to it."],[2268,2414,"Hello, Lambo."],[2435,2552,"Hello, Evelyn!"],[2552,2698,"I'm your new Lamborghini."],[2740,2831,"Please get in."]],"61":[[638,909,"Listen, a Lamborghini supercar just"],[909,1109,"showed up at the Godspeed Racetrack."],[1151,1305,"I need to know who its owner is."],[1322,1459,"The Lamborghini you're asking about"],[1459,1589,"was bought with a card under the name"],[1589,1730,"of the Prince Corp CEO."],[1743,1951,"Prince Corp? Isn't that"],[1951,2152,"the top financial firm in the States?"],[2173,2285,"Wait a minute."],[2306,2427,"I know the CEO."],[2444,2531,"It's Damian!"],[2635,2736,"That's right, sir."],[2802,3048,"I knew it! He's the only one who can"],[3048,3211,"afford something like this."],[3224,3461,"I bought this car with my own money."],[3461,3611,"What's going on?"]],"62":[[1080,1217,"It's all over for you garage guy."],[1309,1401,"Is it really?"],[1422,1539,"The owner of this car"],[1539,1715,"is a guy named Damian."],[1739,1935,"And still, you have the nerve"],[1976,2135,"to claim it was yours."],[2152,2298,"Who is this Damian?"],[2335,2402,"Who is he?"],[2469,2590,"He's the last man"],[2590,2823,"you'd want to cross in all of Vegas."],[2890,3186,"Oh, you're talking about that Damian?"],[3207,3332,"I sure am."],[3386,3636,"CEO of Prince Corp and"],[3670,3878,"son of the wealthiest man"],[3878,4099,"in the world, Jett Hawkings."],[4162,4291,"Oh, right."],[4375,4441,"That Damian."],[4479,4592,"As if the name Damian would"],[4592,4808,"mean anything to you, old man."],[4829,4896,"Why wouldn't it?"],[4904,4979,"He's my son."],[5242,5430,"I'm the one who gave him that name."]],"63":[[12,233,"Mr. Hawkings, what are you talking about?"],[233,304,"This..."],[312,412,"this Damian, he's the"],[412,538,"richest man in the States."],[554,775,"Not even my family moves in his circle."],[792,913,"You have to be very careful"],[913,1030,"when speaking his name."],[1046,1288,"Evelyn, I told you. He's my son."],[1347,1509,"I can talk about him however I like."],[1551,1751,"Mr. Hawkings, you can ignore"],[1751,1906,"everything else I say, but you have"],[1906,2060,"to trust me on this one."],[2097,2227,"Damian is notorious"],[2227,2335,"for having a bad temper"],[2335,2373,"and,"],[2435,2615,"and he runs very shady business."],[2635,2790,"They call him the Devil of Vegas."],[2806,2923,"So, if he found out"],[2923,3078,"that you claimed to be his father,"],[3165,3332,"he would make minced meat out of you."],[3332,3470,"What kinds of shady businesses?"],[3470,3620,"Damien's always been a good kid."],[3641,3741,"You're saying people are going around"],[3741,3828,"calling him the Devil?"],[3916,4058,"Did you just hear him?"],[4087,4391,"He called the most feared man"],[4433,4571,"\"a good kid\"."],[4587,4746,"The old man's off his rocker."],[4763,4934,"And whatever brain cells he has left"],[4934,5096,"after Damian's done with him,"],[5096,5259,"they'll be fried to a crisp."]],"64":[[133,229,"Ev, you should"],[229,304,"really put some"],[304,392,"distance between yourself"],[408,663,"and this repair man. I would really hate"],[663,742,"to see you get dragged"],[742,804,"down with him."],[871,938,"Mr. Hawkings,"],[975,1051,"you don't have to"],[1051,1163,"pretend to know Damian."],[1230,1426,"It's only gonna get you in big trouble."],[1463,1697,"Evelyn, I'm not pretending."],[1697,1805,"Damian is my son."],[1805,1931,"God, this mechanic's"],[1931,2064,"such a lost cause."],[2064,2268,"I've never met such a delusional bullshitter"],[2268,2406,"in my whole life."],[2406,2535,"It's time we expose you"],[2535,2677,"for who you really are,"],[2677,2794,"garage guy."],[2794,2952,"I'm gonna call up Damian and"],[2952,3065,"have him come over."],[3065,3115,"And when he"],[3115,3286,"gets here, you're fucking"],[3286,3324,"dead!"],[4504,4621,"Who is it?"]],"65":[[16,204,"Oh, god...."],[709,796,"Who is it?"],[813,913,"Oh hey, Damian."],[946,1067,"You remember me?"],[1092,1163,"Xavier?"],[1251,1372,"Anyways, I'm here at"],[1372,1501,"the Godspeed Racetrack."],[1530,1685,"And there's some asshole here"],[1685,1860,"who's claiming to be your dad."],[1868,2047,"And he won't shut up."],[2289,2360,"Someone's..."],[2464,2694,"impersonating my father?"],[3399,3486,"Call the racetrack."],[3641,3799,"Have them shut their gates,"],[3799,4104,"and do not let anybody leave."],[4104,4291,"And if anybody tries to leave,"],[4291,4354,"I want you to"],[4354,4625,"knock their fucking teeth out!"],[4713,4771,"You got it, boss."]],"66":[[16,66,"Ha!"],[75,175,"That seals it."],[183,325,"You're good as dead, old man."],[333,496,"You're horrible, Xavier."],[508,604,"How dare you snitch on"],[604,721,"Mr. Hawkings like that?"],[721,892,"I do whatever the fuck I please."],[905,1101,"And when Damian gets down here,"],[1101,1217,"all bets are off."],[1217,1305,"Even your family might"],[1305,1443,"get dragged into this."],[1443,1572,"The next thing you know,"],[1572,1797,"your father is going to be begging me"],[1818,2102,"to marry you to escape Damian's wrath."],[2131,2248,"Ev, if your dad finds out"],[2248,2406,"that you pissed Damian off,"],[2431,2531,"he's really going to start"],[2531,2631,"cracking the whip."],[2635,2744,"You've got to break up with your"],[2744,2948,"repairman boyfriend before it's too late."],[2969,3144,"Mr. Hawkings, what are you doing?"],[3169,3353,"You should leave before it's too late."],[3386,3524,"I'll have someone escort you out, okay?"],[3578,3699,"Everybody listen up!"],[3828,3978,"Nobody's going anywhere."]],"67":[[12,158,"Everybody listen up!"],[166,350,"Nobody's going anywhere."],[371,542,"Not until the Devil of Vegas gets here."],[592,746,"Evelyn, how about this?"],[788,934,"You and I become a couple."],[984,1109,"And, in exchange,"],[1222,1313,"I put in a good word"],[1313,1514,"for you and your family."],[1564,1747,"And get you out of this pickle."],[1755,1985,"If you refuse, you and the entire"],[1985,2152,"Grant family go down"],[2152,2318,"with this dirtbag mechanic."],[2389,2548,"Xavier, you're such a jerk!"],[2686,2827,"See, the thing is Xavier,"],[2919,3023,"The only one who's going to be"],[3023,3132,"in a pickle"],[3199,3269,"is you."],[3424,3728,"The name's Xavier. I'm Damian's friend."],[3812,3916,"Nice to meet you, Xavier."]],"68":[[116,312,"I didn't fucking ask."],[462,583,"Xavier! Xavier!"],[642,738,"Oh my God!"],[738,863,"Xavier!"],[917,1017,"Xavier!"],[1117,1305,"What the hell are you doing?"],[1305,1493,"I thought you worked for Damian."],[1497,1559,"You literally just"],[1559,1672,"almost killed his friend."],[1680,1814,"Oh, that's his friend, huh?"],[2423,2573,"I work for the man. You don't think I know"],[2573,2702,"who his fucking friends are?"],[2756,2852,"And you."],[2869,2990,"Who the hell do you think you are,"],[2990,3069,"acting like you're"],[3069,3182,"one of Damian's friends, huh?"],[3228,3395,"Sir, I am his friend."],[3436,3528,"Ask Damian."],[3532,3716,"I'm not here to bicker about who is"],[3716,3912,"or isn't friends with the boss."],[3924,4054,"These are Damian's orders."],[4112,4333,"Anyone tries to leave this garage..."],[4404,4629,"gets their goddamn teeth knocked out."],[4742,4892,"My son Damian is really"],[4892,4992,"the Devil of Vegas?"]],"69":[[166,258,"Damian is really this"],[258,387,"Devil of Vegas?"],[775,938,"Hey, you old sack of shit."],[938,1046,"Keep my boss's name"],[1046,1151,"out your fucking mouth."],[1305,1559,"Mr. Hawkings, I told you to be careful."],[1601,1772,"Please let me handle this, okay?"],[1935,2043,"Um, sir."],[2239,2331,"My apologies."],[2331,2406,"My..."],[2427,2560,"my friend here, he"],[2590,2811,"he sometimes speaks without thinking."],[2898,3111,"Really, Ev? You're still defending him?"],[3153,3336,"Come on, Ev, just ditch this stupid"],[3336,3449,"grease monkey. I mean,"],[3449,3561,"you're digging your own grave."],[3591,3741,"Listen, baby."],[3774,3916,"He could be the second coming"],[3916,4158,"of Jesus fucking Christ for all I care."],[4162,4254,"Anybody who talks"],[4254,4433,"about my boss like that,"],[4500,4729,"him, and anyone who stands with him,"],[4775,4900,"are fucking dead."]],"70":[[0,120,"So tell me,"],[262,412,"when did Damian become..."],[492,646,"such a ruthless savage?"],[692,1042,"Say that one more time."],[1455,1726,"Look, I don't have time to play games"],[1739,1972,"with little minions like you."],[2006,2160,"All I'm saying is,"],[2193,2377,"if he's such a ruthless savage,"],[2406,2515,"I'm worried about"],[2702,2865,"what will happen to all of you"],[2890,3023,"when he gets here."],[3115,3249,"What's gonna happen to us?"],[3282,3424,"This mechanic's really"],[3424,3532,"gone off the deep end, huh?"],[3586,3720,"There's nothing more I'd like than"],[3720,3824,"to tear your old ass into"],[3824,3983,"a million pieces right now."],[4020,4220,"I'm gonna leave that fun for the boss."],[4512,4650,"Speak of the devil."]],"71":[[0,133,"Speak of the devil."],[358,525,"That's him! Damian's here!"],[671,871,"Mr. Hawkings, why didn't you leave"],[871,1000,"when you had a chance?"],[1021,1163,"Damian's going to kill us!"],[1213,1305,"Trust me."],[1322,1484,"There's nothing to worry about."],[1789,1960,"You made it!"],[2252,2339,"Which one of you"],[2339,2519,"worthless piles of shit"],[2619,2902,"beat my tenth best lap time?"],[2919,2982,"That was me."],[3340,3524,"You filthy little bastard!"],[3557,3807,"My name was up on that board for years!"],[3883,4003,"And now it's gone!"],[4058,4149,"I didn't know"],[4149,4291,"that you were in tenth place."],[4337,4508,"I am so sorry."],[4508,4679,"I, I had a penalty on that lap."],[4679,4804,"I'll ask them to change it."],[4913,4971,"It's fine."],[5046,5121,"You're just lucky"],[5221,5355,"I'm in a good mood today."],[5355,5609,"So, that was you that called me earlier."]],"72":[[70,371,"Yes. As I said on the phone,"],[379,625,"there's some deranged lunatic here"],[642,825,"who's pretending to be your father."],[825,892,"We were just about to"],[892,1042,"beat some sense into him."],[1105,1288,"Yeah. My father retired years ago"],[1288,1438,"from racing, so this track"],[1438,1593,"is the last place that you'd find him."],[1630,1789,"Exactly! That's why"],[1789,1918,"I knew it couldn't be him!"],[2006,2264,"Alright. Let's find that fucker"],[2264,2419,"that's impersonating my father."],[2698,2769,"Alright."],[2948,3257,"Which one of you dim little dipshits"],[3257,3390,"is impersonating my father?"],[4104,4204,"Well, that'd be me."],[4320,4391,"Dad!"]],"73":[[29,100,"Dad!"],[137,371,"Wha- what did you just call him?"],[487,546,"What, are you deaf"],[546,671,"or stupid or something?"],[759,875,"That's my father."],[880,1000,"Jett Hawkings, the richest,"],[1000,1176,"most powerful man on Earth."],[1405,1564,"Mr. Hawkings?"],[1634,1789,"So it's true."],[1822,1939,"I tried to tell you."],[2001,2085,"Dad, why didn't you tell me"],[2085,2181,"you were coming to Vegas?"],[2198,2289,"I would have had one of my boys"],[2289,2414,"here pick you up from the airport."],[2431,2464,"It's fine."],[2548,2631,"My plane landed here"],[2640,2744,"on the track last night."],[2790,2907,"It was a productive trip, too."],[2940,3215,"I was finally able to learn about"],[3215,3415,"my son's shady business"],[3461,3528,"that he's been doing"],[3528,3636,"behind my back."],[3720,3832,"What are you talking about?"],[3832,3903,"Save it."],[3962,4108,"You and I are going to talk later."],[4187,4354,"Now, if I heard correctly,"],[4441,4550,"you were going to"],[4621,4767,"beat some sense into me."],[4817,4904,"Is that right?"],[4975,5059,"Mr. Hawkings."],[5142,5192,"I'm sorry."],[5271,5372,"I should not have judged"],[5372,5492,"a book by its cover."],[5497,5605,"I had no idea that"],[5605,5780,"you were Damian's dad."],[5830,6047,"Please, please forgive me."],[6081,6139,"Please?"],[6168,6268,"Now you're sorry, huh?"],[6377,6519,"Weren't you spewing threats"],[6519,6660,"just a minute ago?"],[7244,7520,"Anyone who disrespects my father"],[7545,7620,"is going to wish"],[7628,7699,"that they were dead!"]],"74":[[12,79,"Anyone"],[79,262,"that disrespects my father is"],[262,375,"gonna wish that they were dead!"],[571,688,"Get this human filth"],[688,804,"out of my fucking sight."],[1109,1151,"No!"],[1155,1276,"Xavier, no!"],[1351,1476,"Please, no!"],[1488,1597,"I didn't mean to!"],[1614,1739,"Please forgive me!"],[1881,2022,"The two of you were pretty full of"],[2022,2198,"yourselves before my son showed up."],[2289,2406,"No, no, no, Mr. Hawkings,"],[2406,2615,"we, we, we are so sorry."],[2615,2761,"We will never let that happen again."],[2786,2852,"You're right."],[2886,2982,"It won't."],[2982,3190,"Look, you two are still young,"],[3240,3390,"so I'll cut you some slack."],[3482,3666,"But if I hear anything about you giving"],[3666,3862,"Evelyn a hard time,"],[3895,4083,"there'll be consequences."],[4141,4254,"Ok. - Ok."],[4275,4408,"Understood."],[4971,5121,"So now you believe me?"],[5121,5288,"You know exactly who I am?"],[5359,5509,"You're that..."],[5584,5693,"Jett Hawkings."],[5693,5885,"You're the richest man in the world."],[5914,6039,"I tried to tell you."],[6085,6327,"Dad, you're never in Vegas anymore."],[6327,6368,"Why don't we just"],[6485,6581,"hop in my car, alright,"],[6581,6744,"and we go see the sights?"],[6856,7182,"Son, step outside with me."],[7278,7503,"We have things to discuss."]],"75":[[1355,1522,"I know what you've been up to, Damian."],[1689,1885,"You think that because you're a Hawkings,"],[1910,2039,"that gives you a free license"],[2039,2181,"to abuse your power?"],[2235,2356,"To run around Vegas"],[2356,2481,"like you own the city."],[2515,2690,"You think that your last name gives you a"],[2769,2927,"get out of jail free card."],[3048,3086,"I don't know what"],[3086,3228,"you're talking about, Dad."],[3244,3357,"I mean, whoever's telling you this"],[3357,3520,"is just slandering me."],[3524,3620,"Okay, that's just bullshit."],[3628,3732,"Alright? It's not true."],[3791,3874,"You know, when they said"],[3874,3987,"you were the Devil of Vegas,"],[3987,4091,"I didn't believe it."],[4262,4396,"But now I see it."],[4491,4688,"This man standing in front of me,"],[4750,4850,"is not the well-behaved,"],[4850,4992,"respectful son I raised."],[5059,5138,"Not anymore."],[5159,5305,"I can explain everything."],[5376,5601,"Okay, great, because I would"],[5601,5834,"love to hear this explanation."],[5901,6047,"How about we start with your orders"],[6047,6218,"to shut down this race track and"],[6218,6348,"knock the teeth out of anybody"],[6348,6423,"who tries to leave,"],[6423,6619,"not to mention your little minion here"],[6627,6777,"kicking and slapping people"],[6777,6906,"the second he stepped in."],[6940,7107,"I would love to hear this explanation."]],"76":[[20,108,"What are you talking about?"],[333,483,"You. Come here."],[588,675,"What’s up, boss?"],[721,871,"What the fuck?"],[930,1026,"I tell you to remain"],[1026,1176,"peaceful and polite."],[1201,1276,"And now, I hear you're"],[1276,1355,"going around kicking..."],[1426,1576,"and slapping people?"],[1614,1764,"Boss, I thought you wanted me to."],[1906,2056,"He wants me to take the fall."],[2089,2206,"I'm sorry."],[2206,2348,"It's my mistake."],[2348,2473,"Yeah, it's your fucking mistake."],[2473,2602,"Now get the fuck out of here."],[2823,2973,"See that?"],[2994,3082,"It's just a simple case"],[3082,3232,"of insubordination."],[3303,3336,"All right. Look."],[3336,3403,"Fine, fine, fine."],[3403,3482,"I'll make sure that he's"],[3482,3566,"properly reprimanded."],[3591,3678,"Okay?"],[3737,3858,"Now, look, you and I haven't had"],[3858,4054,"some proper father-son time"],[4054,4204,"in a while, so tell you what?"],[4204,4362,"Why don’t I get my car,"],[4362,4500,"we go out to the town-"],[4500,4600,"Do you think I've gone senile"],[4600,4667,"or something?"],[4771,4859,"Thought I wouldn’t"],[4859,4996,"figure out what you've become."],[5155,5296,"Son, you're not getting off so easy."]],"77":[[50,145,"Two can play this game."],[191,262,"What do you mean?"],[296,496,"Don't you think you overdid it just a"],[496,625,"little bit right there, Dad?"],[658,729,"You overdid what?"],[750,804,"You just gave me"],[804,946,"a fucking mouthful in"],[946,1034,"front of my own men."],[1113,1192,"Alright, do you have any idea"],[1192,1359,"how weak that makes me look?"],[1388,1530,"That can affect my fucking business!"],[1543,1664,"Your business?"],[1743,1985,"Your shady mafia business!"],[2185,2385,"I give you the keys"],[2477,2565,"to Prince Corp."],[2610,2698,"What do you do?"],[2748,2882,"You get yourself involved"],[2882,3153,"in underground black market dealings."],[3153,3274,"No, Dad."],[3303,3440,"It's not what it looks like, alright?"],[3520,3695,"I'm in my Wolf of Wall Street"],[3724,3895,"phase now, okay?"],[3937,4037,"It's all in good fun."],[4037,4195,"I'm not breaking any laws."],[4208,4341,"And even if I was,"],[4341,4421,"I mean,"],[4450,4671,"you're my Dad, right?"],[4725,4879,"You can just bail me out, right?"],[4942,5130,"You still don't regret your actions."]],"78":[[58,371,"I'm gonna say this one time."],[513,579,"One time only."],[713,809,"If you keep this up,"],[921,1076,"you're gonna ruin your life."],[1134,1184,"You're really fucking"],[1184,1292,"pushing it now, Dad."],[1326,1443,"Alright, I know you're my pops,"],[1443,1589,"and everything and you feel obligated"],[1589,1739,"to just give me advice whenever"],[1739,1856,"you fucking feel like it."],[1856,2014,"but let's face it, okay?"],[2127,2273,"You fucking boomers"],[2285,2419,"are just out of touch."],[2498,2610,"This world just is"],[2610,2815,"not the same as it used to be."],[2877,2986,"Damian."],[3044,3336,"You are a sorry excuse for a son."],[3486,3832,"And I will be damned if I let you"],[3878,4195,"tear down everything that I built."]],"79":[[0,141,"And I'll be damned"],[216,321,"if I let you"],[329,462,"tear down everything"],[517,600,"that I built."],[754,875,"Jesus, Dad, just take a"],[875,1055,"fucking chill pill, okay?"],[1117,1267,"I'm an adult now."],[1267,1401,"Okay? I have my own morals."],[1418,1534,"My own values."],[1593,1672,"Alright?"],[1726,1826,"Plus, I mean..."],[1926,2177,"How many businesses do we have, right?"],[2218,2398,"I mean, one secret small business"],[2398,2577,"isn't gonna cause us any harm."],[2598,2711,"Damian."],[2831,2944,"Admit it."],[3019,3186,"You fucked up."],[3228,3307,"Right now..."],[3457,3591,"this is the last chance I'm giving you."],[3737,3949,"Jesus fucking Christ! Okay, fine!"],[3958,4095,"I fucked up, okay?"],[4104,4229,"Is that what you wanna fucking hear?"],[4241,4454,"I fucked up! There!"],[4500,4617,"I said it!"],[4646,4838,"Okay? Jesus!"],[4959,5080,"Alright, listen, Dad."],[5150,5255,"Are we done here?"],[5271,5376,"Cause I gotta go."],[5580,5684,"Stop!"]],"80":[[29,162,"What now? Alright?"],[162,254,"I thought we were finished."],[321,392,"As of today"],[496,563,"all your bank accounts"],[563,688,"and credit cards are frozen."],[971,1084,"Let's see how far this..."],[1188,1330,"Wolf of Wall Street phase"],[1372,1534,"gets you without any of my money."],[1659,1805,"Alright, Jesus, Dad."],[1818,1893,"Look, I know you're not"],[1893,2027,"gonna fucking do anything."],[2047,2147,"So just..."],[2210,2352,"quit it. Okay?"],[2540,2619,"Alright, seriously."],[2635,2823,"Knock it off. It's not funny anymore."],[2873,3002,"If I don't put an end to this now,"],[3002,3132,"sooner or later"],[3194,3278,"you'll do something that"],[3278,3436,"there's no coming back from."],[4162,4233,"Fuck!"]],"81":[[50,412,"Fuck! Jesus fucking... fuck!"],[412,483,"God fucking-"],[483,642,"You really fucking did it, didn't you?"],[642,779,"You froze my fucking account!"],[992,1067,"What?"],[1130,1234,"Sir, the board"],[1234,1388,"has just issued an order to remove you"],[1388,1530,"from your position at Prince Corp,"],[1530,1693,"effective immediately."],[1693,1881,"Fuck!"],[1881,2147,"God fucking damn it!"],[2202,2435,"Good luck funding your side business."],[2627,2936,"Damian, I think what you need now is..."],[3144,3407,"time to reflect on what you've done."],[3428,3591,"So why don't you go on home."],[3641,3778,"Just sit in your own thoughts"],[3778,3878,"for a while"],[3958,4133,"and when you're ready,"],[4216,4433,"come on out. Be a better man."],[4771,4896,"Fuck."]],"82":[[492,588,"Mr. Hawkings,"],[588,825,"you don't have to be so tough on him."],[859,967,"He's still your son."],[1034,1121,"It's my fault."],[1176,1238,"I should have been"],[1238,1334,"a better father to him."],[1680,1789,"There's still time to put him"],[1789,1885,"on the right path."],[2419,2460,"Watch out!"],[2619,2865,"Mr. Hawkings, your... your hand."],[3123,3224,"I am still pretending."],[3653,3691,"What do you say"],[3691,3795,"I take you for a little ride?"]]}